# CareerLaunch FEATURE TIER POLICY
## Tier notes
- owner の基本導線は Free でも成立させる
- Free では応募実行開始までを成立させる
- Pro に求人別最適化 / 出力 / 面接準備 / 文面強化を集約する
- current canonical plan count = 2
- Business tier is removed from current canonical pricing decision

## Free
- basic resume drafting
- basic work history drafting
- application position register with count limit
- basic checklist
- basic memo
- basic AI assist with light limit

## Pro
- job specific optimization
- unlimited application position management
- interview prep pack
- interview Q&A drafting
- thank you / decline / schedule adjustment message drafting
- PDF / DOCX export
- stronger AI assist
- priority support

## Non goal
- Business tier を前提にした 3階建て課金は current canonical design では採用しない
